## Description {#details}

Helper for printing DanglingDebugInfo.

This hoop-jumping is to store a <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/value">Value</a> pointer, so that we can print a whole DDI as one object. Call SelectionDAGBuilder::printDDI instead of using directly.
